.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Nationality: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. Nationality:turkish is between Hobby:reading and Nationality:colombian##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Nationality:british##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Nationality:british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

