Sport: basketball, biathlon, rugby, tennis
1. Sport:biathlon == Pet:lizard##1
2. Pet:cat is between Sport:basketball and Pet:rat##2
3. Sport:biathlon is on the far right##1
4. Pet:cat is on the right of Sport:rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Sport   | rugby | tennis | basketball | biathlon |

